history.content:
CS Advising drop in hours will end at 2pm tomorrow as our team will be headed to a special training. We will be available in Soda Hall from 10am to 12pm and 1pm-2pm.

Students can make an appointment with a CS advisor through the appointments portal in CalCentral or email cs-advising@cs.berkeley.edu with any questions.

Thank you.
